# patterns/ — curated by Eratosthenes

Reusable techniques and solution shapes that worked across multiple sessions or
multiple apps. Promoted here after at least one specialist confirmed the pattern
holds beyond its original context.

Each file is named `<short-kebab-title>.md` and contains: the pattern, when it
applies, a concrete example from apex-research work, and "known exceptions".

Do not write to this directory. Submit via Protocol A — see common-prompt.md.
